main event: Three officers sighted an unidentified object moving rapidly across the sky from east to southwest.
interesting points: The object was observed at a bearing of 123 position angle and was accelerating and ascending,The initial brightness of the object was slightly brighter than first magnitude and then steadily diminishing,The sighting involved credible military observers,The object was definitely not an aircraft or shooting star,There was speculation the object could be a Russian Mars shot due to favorable conditions reported in the news.
sighted object: unidentified object or light in the sky
